				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">格内薇芙扔出爆竹，造成<span color="#ff9999">160%,40%</span><span>伤害。<br/></span><span color="#ffe599">提升后：</span><span>伤害获得提升，爆竹造成</span><span color="#ff9999">240%,40%x4</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
